Class PageObjectUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.imaginea.test.automation.framework.util.Utilities
      • org.imaginea.test.automation.framework.util.PageObjectUtils
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractPageClass, Browser, TestClass

    public abstract class PageObjectUtils
extends Utilities
    Utility class containing mainly the util methods for the Page Class and Locator class. Not meant to be used by other classes.

      • getPageObject

        public <T> T getPageObject(Class<?> pageClass,
                  File customLocatorFile)
        Utility to create and get the said page class object. This utility directly creates the said page class object and returns it. No navigation or verification is done for the said page.

        This method initializes any PageFactory based WebElements present in the said class using the provided locator file.

        Parameters:
        pageClass - Page class extending PageClass for which the object has to be created and returned.
        customLocatorFile - - File object of the file containing the key/value pair of the locators.
        Returns:
        The said page class object

        public <T> T to(Class<?> pageClass)

        pageClass - - Page class extending PageClass to where the driver have to be navigated.
        Returns:
        The said page class object once verification is successful.
